Attribute.Name: AgentCriteriaId
Attribute.Description: The unique identifier of an agent criterion.

Attribute.Name: MessageXml
Attribute.Description: A criterion used by an agent for selecting the records to process.

Attribute.Name: TransactionKey
Attribute.Description: The transaction key that is associated with this agent criteria.

Element.Description: This is the same as the data present in the MessageXml attribute of AgentCriteria, and will contain the same child elements and attributes as that XML. It will be returned only if the MessageXml attribute is in the template.
